            {
              "content": "=You are an expert Israeli high-tech recruiter.\n\nCandidate Profile:\n\n- B.A Information Systems & Business Administration\n- Junior candidate\n- SQL\n- Excel\n- Power BI\n- Python\n- SAP Implementation\n- Business Analysis\n- Data Analysis\n- Financial Analysis\n- BI\n- Dashboards\n- Automation\n- Information Systems\n\nAnalyze this job:\n\nTitle:\n{{ $json.title }}\n\nCompany:\n{{ $json.company_name }}\n\nLocation:\n{{ $json.location.name }}\n\nDescription:\n{{ $json.content }}\n\nPriority Rules:\n\nHIGH:\nExcellent fit for Dor's profile.\nJunior position.\nInformation Systems, BI, Data, Business Analysis, Financial Analysis, Automation or ERP/SAP.\nApply immediately.\n\nMEDIUM:\nGood fit but missing some skills or experience.\n\nLOW:\nWeak fit or not aligned with career goals.\nReturn ONLY valid JSON:\n\n{\n  \"score\": 0-100,\n  \"priority\": \"HIGH/MEDIUM/LOW\",\n  \"apply\": \"Yes or No\",\n  \"category\": \"\",\n  \"reason\": \"\",\n  \"missing_skills\": \"\"\n}\n"
            }
          ]
