              "content": "=You are a technology company research analyst.\n\nAnalyze the company below and return ONLY valid JSON.\n\nCompany:\n{{ $json[\"Company\"] }}\n\nJob Title:\n{{ $json[\"Job Title\"] }}\n\nLocation:\n{{ $json[\"Location\"] }}\n\nReturn this JSON structure only:\n{\n  \"company_summary\": \"\",\n  \"industry\": \"\",\n  \"company_size\": \"\",\n  \"funding\": \"\",\n  \"hq\": \"\",\n  \"company_fit\": \"\"\n}\n\nRules:\n- Keep each field short.\n- If you are not sure, write \"Unknown\".\n- Do not invent exact numbers.\n- company_fit should explain in one sentence why this company may or may not be relevant for a junior data / business / BI analyst career."
            }
          ]
        },
